		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="132768"></a><b>itchyban</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Sage<br /><img src="images/avatars/8085224943edfb6609d366.jpg" alt="" border="0" /><br /><br />Joined: 13 Mar 2003<br />Posts: 2575<br /></span><br /></td>
		<td class="row2" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=132768&amp;sid=f80b1822727d8773628db1ebdfbffbfe#132768"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Feb 02, 2004 11:34 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Waiting For Loot -- The Depressing News</span></td>
			        <td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="ignore.php?mode=add&amp;username=itchyban&amp;topic=11304&amp;sid=f80b1822727d8773628db1ebdfbffbfe"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_ignore.gif" alt="Add User to Ignore List" title="Add User to Ignore List" border="0" /></a> <a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=132768&amp;sid=f80b1822727d8773628db1ebdfbffbfe"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
