				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm not sure if im understanding this correctly but you are saying that over time your chances of a item drop increase? Thats false if your speaking by true math of using "chance" Its like a flipping a coin 10 times, you can get heads 9 times in a row and that 10th time whats the chance you get tails? 50/50 still, doesnt matter how many times you got heads in a row it doesnt change any thing until you get into very spacific propability (spelling) stuff.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=742948" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ghetoman Totherescue's Gear</a>
